In Baltimore City, the Sheriff shall receive an expense allowance of $750 two times per year and a salary of:
$79,300 in calendar year 2007;
$84,600 in calendar year 2008;
$89,900 in calendar year 2009;
$95,200 in calendar year 2010; and
In calendar year 2011 and thereafter, no less than the salary of a Command Staff 2 in the Baltimore City Police Department at the midpoint in the pay scale.

