The Sheriff of Kent County shall receive a salary of:
$67,000 for the calendar year 2009;
$68,000 for the calendar year 2010;
$82,000 for the calendar year 2011;
$83,000 for the calendar year 2012;
$84,000 for the calendar year 2013; and
